## Migration plan (post-7A.5)

1. Land this file under `src/lib/env.ts`.
2. Add `import { env, isProd } from "@/lib/env"` to one route at a time (start with `src/app/api/cron/morning-brief/route.ts`).
3. Replace `process.env.X!` with `env.X` and `process.env.NODE_ENV === "production"` with `isProd()`.
4. Each migration is a one-file PR; CI catches schema mismatches at type-check time.
5. Once all 52 sites use `env`, delete the loose `process.env.*!` pattern from `eslint.config` rules.
